Class BasicCIntegerType

  • java.lang.Object
    • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicType
      • sun.jvm.hotspot.types.basic.BasicCIntegerType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CIntegerType, Type

    public class BasicCIntegerType
extends BasicType
implements CIntegerType

    This specialization of BasicType implements the CIntegerType interface and describes all C integer types.
